  "special": {
    "title": "I can have such a thing?",
    "description": "Always Shock. Shots explode on impact for splash damage, then spawn a lightning orb that rises and detonates again. The first blast scales with grenade damage bonuses, while the second does not."
  },
  "notes": "As a Shock weapon, it can damage the user. With the Transformer, self-hits can refill the shield and may also be absorbed as launcher ammo. Other absorb shields only have a chance to convert the hit into launcher ammo. The second detonation can be amplified by amp shields. The initial splash benefits from grenade damage bonuses, but the rising orb's follow-up blast does not. The orb only appears if the first hit connects with an enemy or with a ledge or edge.",
